title: 2BR, 1BA: Excellent SOMA Location near BART & Downtown
posting_body: ['Spacious 2 bedroom and 1 bathroom apartment in the heart of SOMA and near BART and Downtown SF.', 'It is located near 8th and Howard Street approx.', '2 short blocks to Market St and BART.', 'Apartment features:', '- Full kitchen with electric stove, microwave, fridge', '- Hardwood floors throughout', '- 2 Bedrooms each have large closets', '- Living room has large windows', '- Safe and secure building', '- Shared coin operated laundry', 'No smoking.', 'No pets.', 'No smoking in apartment or building.', 'No parking is available.', 'Street parking only.', 'No elevator in building.', 'Terms: Must move in within next 30 days; 12 month term then month-to-month; Tenant pays PG&E and water', 'Move-in fees: First month (will pro-rate for partial month) + last month rent deposit + $1900 security deposit.', 'Applicants will need to complete application and provide references and background checks.', 'If interested, please reply with your desired move-in date and full contact info.', 'Otherwise, your email will be disregarded.']
